<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>C Programming - LearnHub</title>
  <style>
    /* Global Styles */
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
      background: #f4f4f9;
      color: #2c3e50;
    }

    h1, h2 {
      font-weight: bold;
    }

    /* Navbar Styling */
    nav {
      background: #2c3e50;
      padding: 1rem;
      position: sticky;
      top: 0;
      z-index: 100;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }

    nav .logo {
      font-size: 1.8rem;
      font-weight: bold;
      color: #fff;
    }

    nav ul {
      list-style: none;
      padding: 0;
      display: flex;
    }

    nav ul li {
      margin: 0 1.5rem;
    }

    nav ul li a {
      color: white;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      padding: 0.5rem;
      transition: background 0.3s ease, color 0.3s ease;
    }

    nav ul li a:hover {

      color: #74ebd5;

    }

    /* Main Content */
    .course-details {
      padding: 3rem 2rem;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .course-details h1 {
      font-size: 2.5rem;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    .course-details p {
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    /* Syllabus Section */
    .syllabus {
      max-width: 900px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      text-align: left;
    }

    .syllabus ul {
      list-style: none;
      padding: 0;
    }

    .syllabus li {
      padding: 1rem;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
    }

    .syllabus li:hover {
      background-color: #ecf0f1;
    }

    .syllabus button {
      padding: 0.3rem 0.6rem;
      background: #2c3e50;
      color: white;
      border: none;
      cursor: pointer;
      font-size: 1rem;
      transition: 0.3s;
    }

    .syllabus button:hover {
      background: #74ebd5;
      color: #2c3e50;
    }

    /* Footer */
    footer {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 1rem;
      background: #2c3e50;
      color: white;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
    }

    /* Responsive Styles */
    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      nav ul {
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: center;
      }

      nav ul li {
        margin: 1rem 0;
      }

      .course-details {
        padding: 2rem 1rem;
      }

      .course-details h1 {
        font-size: 2rem;
      }

      .syllabus li {
        padding: 0.8rem;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <!-- Navbar -->
  <nav>
    <div class="logo">LearnHub</div>
    <ul>
      <li><a href="/Home?email=<%=email%>">Home</a></li>
      <li><a href="#" id="Syllabus">Syllabus</a></li>
    </ul>
  </nav>

  <!-- Course Details Section -->
  <div class="course-details" id="Syllabus">
    <h1>C Programming</h1>
    <p>
      Master the fundamentals of C programming, including algorithms, data structures, and memory management.
    </p>

    <h2>Syllabus</h2>
    <div class="syllabus">
      <ul>
        <li>Introduction to C Programming <a href="/course/C%20Programming/Introduction/<%=email%>"><button>Explore</button></a></li>
        <li>Variables, Data Types, and Operators <button>Explore</button></li>
        <li>Control Structures (if-else, loops) <button>Explore</button></li>
        <li>Functions and Recursion <button>Explore</button></li>
        <li>Arrays and Strings <button>Explore</button></li>
        <li>Pointers and Memory Management <button>Explore</button></li>
        <li>Structures and Unions <button>Explore</button></li>
        <li>File Handling in C <button>Explore</button></li>
        <li>Advanced Topics and Projects <button>Explore</button></li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Footer Section -->
  <footer>
    <p>&copy; 2025 LearnHub. All rights reserved.</p>
  </footer>

</body>
</html>
